        "Description": "Cristina Dionisi, an acclaimed Italian singer, has been found out by our client that she has been stealing their music and selling it as her own. Costing our client millions. Unbeknownst to her adoring fans, her upcoming performance in Sapienza will be her last.\r\rThe Agency has suggested you take a sniper rifle with you and use the bell tower of the church as a vantage point to eliminate your target.\r\rGood luck, Hitman.",
